#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.reindex.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.reindex"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:1 of
msgid "Conform Series/DataFrame to new index with optional filling logic."
msgstr "使 Series/DataFrame 符合新的索引，并可选择填充逻辑。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:3 of
msgid ""
"Places NA/NaN in locations having no value in the previous index. A new "
"object is produced unless the new index is equivalent to the current one "
"and ``copy=False``."
msgstr ""
"在先前索引中没有值的位置放置 NA/NaN。除非新索引与当前索引等价且 ``copy="
"False``，否则会生成一个新对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:7 of
msgid "New labels / index to conform the axis specified by 'axis' to."
msgstr "要使由 'axis' 指定的轴符合的新标签/索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:9
#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:12 of
msgid ""
"New labels / index to conform to, should be specified using keywords. "
"Preferably an Index object to avoid duplicating data."
msgstr "要符合的新标签/索引，应使用关键字指定。最好使用 Index 对象以避免重复数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:15 of
msgid ""
"Axis to target. Can be either the axis name ('index', 'columns') or "
"number (0, 1)."
msgstr "目标轴。可以是轴名称（'index', 'columns'）或数字（0, 1）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:18 of
msgid ""
"Method to use for filling holes in reindexed DataFrame. Please note: this"
" is only applicable to DataFrames/Series with a monotonically "
"increasing/decreasing index.  * None (default): don't fill gaps * pad / "
"ffill: Propagate last valid observation forward to next   valid. * "
"backfill / bfill: Use next valid observation to fill gap. * nearest: Use "
"nearest valid observations to fill gap."
msgstr ""
"用于在重新索引的 DataFrame 中填充空洞的方法。请注意：这仅适用于具有单调"
"递增/递减索引的 DataFrame/Series。  * None（默认）：不填充空隙 * pad / "
"ffill：将最后一个有效观测值向前传播到下一个有效值。 * backfill / bfill："
"使用下一个有效观测值填充空隙。 * nearest：使用最近的有效观测值填充空隙。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:18 of
msgid ""
"Method to use for filling holes in reindexed DataFrame. Please note: this"
" is only applicable to DataFrames/Series with a monotonically "
"increasing/decreasing index."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:22 of
msgid "None (default): don't fill gaps"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:23 of
msgid "pad / ffill: Propagate last valid observation forward to next valid."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:25 of
msgid "backfill / bfill: Use next valid observation to fill gap."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:26 of
msgid "nearest: Use nearest valid observations to fill gap."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:28 of
msgid "Return a new object, even if the passed indexes are the same."
msgstr "即使传入的索引相同，也返回一个新对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:30 of
msgid ""
"Broadcast across a level, matching Index values on the passed MultiIndex "
"level."
msgstr "在层级上进行广播，在传入的 MultiIndex 层级上匹配 Index 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:33 of
msgid ""
"Value to use for missing values. Defaults to NaN, but can be any "
"\"compatible\" value."
msgstr "用于缺失值的值。默认为 NaN，但可以是任何“兼容”的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:36 of
msgid "Maximum number of consecutive elements to forward or backward fill."
msgstr "向前或向后填充的最大连续元素数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:38 of
msgid ""
"Maximum distance between original and new labels for inexact matches. The"
" values of the index at the matching locations most satisfy the equation "
"``abs(index[indexer] - target) <= tolerance``.  Tolerance may be a scalar"
" value, which applies the same tolerance to all values, or list-like, "
"which applies variable tolerance per element. List-like includes list, "
"tuple, array, Series, and must be the same size as the index and its "
"dtype must exactly match the index's type."
msgstr ""
"不精确匹配时原始和新标签之间的最大距离。在匹配位置的索引值必须满足方程 ``"
"abs(index[indexer] - target) <= tolerance``。 容差可以是一个标量值，适用"
"于所有值；也可以是类列表，对每个元素应用不同的容差。 类列表包括 list、"
"tuple、array、Series，且必须与索引大小相同，其数据类型必须与索引类型完全"
"匹配。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:38 of
msgid ""
"Maximum distance between original and new labels for inexact matches. The"
" values of the index at the matching locations most satisfy the equation "
"``abs(index[indexer] - target) <= tolerance``."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:42 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Tolerance may be a scalar value, which applies the same tolerance to all "
"values, or list-like, which applies variable tolerance per element. List-"
"like includes list, tuple, array, Series, and must be the same size as "
"the index and its dtype must exactly match the index's type."
msgstr ""
"不精确匹配时原始和新标签之间的最大距离。在匹配位置的索引值必须满足方程 ``"
"abs(index[indexer] - target) <= tolerance``。 容差可以是一个标量值，适用"
"于所有值；也可以是类列表，对每个元素应用不同的容差。 类列表包括 list、"
"tuple、array、Series，且必须与索引大小相同，其数据类型必须与索引类型完全"
"匹配。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

