msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:54 of
msgid "Set row labels."
msgstr "设置行标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:56 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.reset_index`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:57 of
msgid "Remove row labels or move them to new columns."
msgstr "移除行标签或将它们移动到新列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:59 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.reindex_like`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:60 of
msgid "Change to same indices as other DataFrame."
msgstr "改变为与其他 DataFrame 相同的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:63 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:64 of
msgid "``DataFrame.reindex`` supports two calling conventions"
msgstr "``DataFrame.reindex`` 支持两种调用方式"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:66 of
msgid "``(index=index_labels, columns=column_labels, ...)``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:67 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "``(labels, axis={'index', 'columns'}, ...)``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:69 of
msgid "We *highly* recommend using keyword arguments to clarify your intent."
msgstr "我们*强烈*建议使用关键字参数来明确你的意图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:72 of
msgid "Create a dataframe with some fictional data."
msgstr "创建一个包含一些虚构数据的 dataframe。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:87 of
msgid ""
"Create a new index and reindex the dataframe. By default values in the "
"new index that do not have corresponding records in the dataframe are "
"assigned ``NaN``."
msgstr ""
"创建一个新的索引并重新索引 dataframe。默认情况下，新索引中没有对应记录的"
"值会被赋值为 ``NaN``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:101 of
msgid ""
"We can fill in the missing values by passing a value to the keyword "
"``fill_value``. Because the index is not monotonically increasing or "
"decreasing, we cannot use arguments to the keyword ``method`` to fill the"
" ``NaN`` values."
msgstr ""
"我们可以通过向关键字 ``fill_value`` 传递一个值来填充缺失值。由于索引不是"
"单调递增或递减的，我们不能使用关键字 ``method`` 的参数来填充 ``NaN`` 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:122 of
msgid "We can also reindex the columns."
msgstr "我们也可以重新索引列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:132 of
msgid "Or we can use \"axis-style\" keyword arguments"
msgstr "或者我们可以使用“axis-style”关键字参数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:142 of
msgid ""
"To further illustrate the filling functionality in ``reindex``, we will "
"create a dataframe with a monotonically increasing index (for example, a "
"sequence of dates)."
msgstr ""
"为了进一步说明 ``reindex`` 中的填充功能，我们将创建一个具有单调递增索引的"
" dataframe（例如，一系列日期）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:159 of
msgid "Suppose we decide to expand the dataframe to cover a wider date range."
msgstr "假设我们决定扩展 dataframe 以覆盖更广泛的日期范围。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:176 of
msgid ""
"The index entries that did not have a value in the original data frame "
"(for example, '2009-12-29') are by default filled with ``NaN``. If "
"desired, we can fill in the missing values using one of several options."
msgstr ""
"在原始数据框中没有值的索引条目（例如，'2009-12-29'）默认会被填充为 ``NaN`"
"`。如果需要，我们可以使用几种选项之一来填充缺失值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:181 of
msgid ""
"For example, to back-propagate the last valid value to fill the ``NaN`` "
"values, pass ``bfill`` as an argument to the ``method`` keyword."
msgstr ""
"例如，要将最后一个有效值向后传播以填充 ``NaN`` 值，请将 ``bfill`` 作为"
"参数传递给 ``method`` 关键字。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:197 of
msgid ""
"Please note that the ``NaN`` value present in the original dataframe (at "
"index value 2010-01-03) will not be filled by any of the value "
"propagation schemes. This is because filling while reindexing does not "
"look at dataframe values, but only compares the original and desired "
"indexes. If you do want to fill in the ``NaN`` values present in the "
"original dataframe, use the ``fillna()`` method."
msgstr ""
"请注意，原始 dataframe 中存在的 ``NaN`` 值（在索引值 2010-01-03 处）不会"
"被任何值传播方案填充。这是因为重新索引时的填充并不查看 dataframe 的值，而"
"只是比较原始索引和目标索引。如果你确实想要填充原始 dataframe 中的 ``NaN``"
" 值，请使用 ``fillna()`` 方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reindex.reindex:204 of
msgid "See the :ref:`user guide <basics.reindexing>` for more."
msgstr "请参阅 :ref:`用户指南 <basics.reindexing>` 了解更多信息。"

